<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar" dir="rtl">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description" content="دليل القيود غير المحاسبية المؤثرة على قرارات الاستثمار: التمويل، المخاطر، والسيولة.">
    <title>قيود قرارات الاستثمار | منظور استراتيجي</title>

    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Tajawal:wght@300;400;500;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons+Round" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        /* =========================================================
           DESIGN TOKENS
        ========================================================= */
        :root {
            --primary:       #1565C0;
            --primary-light: #1976D2;
            --primary-pale:  #E3F2FD;
            --accent:        #F50057;
            --accent-warm:   #FF6F00;
            --surface:       #FFFFFF;
            --bg:            #F0F4F8;
            --text-main:     #1A1A2E;
            --text-sub:      #546E7A;
            --text-muted:    #90A4AE;
            --radius-card:   16px;
            --radius-pill:   999px;
            --shadow-card:   0 2px 8px rgba(21,101,192,.08), 0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.06);
            --shadow-hover:  0 16px 40px rgba(21,101,192,.18);
            --transition:    all 0.28s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1);
            --font:          'Tajawal', sans-serif;

            /* Reading-mode tokens (overridden by body classes) */
            --page-bg:    #F0F4F8;
            --page-text:  #1A1A2E;
            --card-bg:    #FFFFFF;
            --hero-text:  #FFFFFF;
        }

        /* ── SEPIA MODE ── */
        body.mode-sepia {
            --page-bg:   #F5EDD8;
            --page-text: #3B2A1A;
            --card-bg:   #FBF5E6;
            --primary:   #8B5E3C;
            --primary-pale: #EDE0CC;
            --bg:        #F5EDD8;
        }

        /* ── DARK MODE ── */
        body.mode-dark {
            --page-bg:   #0D1117;
            --page-text: #CDD9E5;
            --card-bg:   #161B22;
            --primary:   #58A6FF;
            --primary-pale: #1C2A3A;
            --bg:        #0D1117;
            --text-sub:  #8B949E;
            --text-muted:#6E7681;
            --shadow-card: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,.4);
            --shadow-hover:0 16px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.6);
        }
        body.mode-dark .hero-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0D2545 0%, #0A3069 100%);
        }
        body.mode-dark .badge-hero {
            background: rgba(88,166,255,.15) !important;
            color: #58A6FF !important;
        }
        body.mode-dark .summary-box {
            background: #161B22;
        }
        body.mode-dark .footer-bar {
            background: #010409;
        }
        body.mode-sepia .hero-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6D4C2A 0%, #9C6B3C 100%);
        }
        body.mode-sepia .summary-box {
            background: #FBF5E6;
        }

        /* =========================================================
           GLOBAL
        ========================================================= */
        *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

        html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

        body {
            font-family: var(--font);
            background-color: var(--page-bg);
            color: var(--page-text);
            line-height: 1.8; /* Increased line-height for better breathing room */
            transition: background-color .4s ease, color .4s ease;
        }

        /* =========================================================
           READING MODE SWITCHER
        ========================================================= */
        .mode-switcher {
            position: fixed;
            top: 18px;
            left: 18px;
            z-index: 1000;
            display: flex;
            gap: 6px;
            background: var(--card-bg);
            padding: 6px 10px;
            border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,.15);
            transition: var(--transition);
        }
        .mode-btn {
            width: 30px;
            height: 30px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 2px solid transparent;
            cursor: pointer;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            transition: var(--transition);
            font-size: 15px;
            background: transparent;
        }
        .mode-btn:hover { transform: scale(1.15); }
        .mode-btn.active { border-color: var(--primary); }
        .mode-btn.btn-light-mode { color: #F9A825; }
        .mode-btn.btn-sepia-mode { color: #8B5E3C; }
        .mode-btn.btn-dark-mode  { color: #58A6FF; }
        .mode-label {
            font-size: 10px;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            align-self: center;
            margin-left: 2px;
            font-family: var(--font);
        }

        /* =========================================================
           FLOATING BUTTONS (PRINT + SCROLL-TOP)
        ========================================================= */
        .fab-group {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 28px;
            left: 28px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 12px;
            z-index: 999;
        }
        .fab {
            width: 52px;
            height: 52px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,.22);
            transition: var(--transition);
            font-size: 22px;
        }
        .fab:hover { transform: scale(1.12) translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 28px rgba(0,0,0,.28); }
        .fab-print  { background: var(--primary); color: #fff; }
        .fab-top    { background: var(--accent); color: #fff; opacity: 0; pointer-events: none; }
        .fab-top.visible { opacity: 1; pointer-events: auto; }
        .fab .material-icons-round { font-size: 24px; }

        /* =========================================================
           HERO
        ========================================================= */
        .hero-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0D47A1 0%, #1976D2 60%, #1E88E5 100%);
            color: #fff;
            padding: 90px 0 70px;
            border-bottom-left-radius: 48px;
            border-bottom-right-radius: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 70px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .hero-section::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -60px; right: -60px;
            width: 300px; height: 300px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,.05);
            border-radius: 50%;
        }
        .hero-section::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -80px; left: -40px;
            width: 220px; height: 220px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,.04);
            border-radius: 50%;
        }
        .badge-hero {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,.18) !important;
            color: #fff !important;
            backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.2);
            font-size: .8rem;
            font-family: var(--font);
            font-weight: 500;
            letter-spacing: .5px;
        }
        .hero-title {
            font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.2rem);
            font-weight: 900;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
            text-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,.2);
        }
        .hero-sub {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            opacity: .82;
            max-width: 660px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .hero-stats {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 40px;
            margin-top: 40px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        .hero-stat {
            text-align: center;
        }
        .hero-stat-num {
            font-size: 2.4rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            line-height: 1;
        }
        .hero-stat-lbl {
            font-size: .78rem;
            opacity: .7;
            margin-top: 4px;
        }

        /* =========================================================
           SECTION HEADING
        ========================================================= */
        .section-heading {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 56px; /* Increased margin */
        }
        .section-eyebrow {
            font-size: .78rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--primary);
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        .section-title {
            font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 2.2rem);
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--page-text);
            position: relative;
            display: inline-block;
        }
        .section-title::after {
            content: '';
            display: block;
            width: 56px;
            height: 4px;
            background: var(--accent);
            border-radius: 2px;
            margin: 14px auto 0;
        }

        /* =========================================================
           CARDS GRID (2 Columns Desktop, 1 Column Mobile)
        ========================================================= */
        .cards-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); /* 2 columns strictly */
            gap: 36px; /* Increased gap for breathing room */
        }

        .constraint-card {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            border-radius: var(--radius-card);
            padding: 34px 30px; /* Increased padding */
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-card);
            transition: var(--transition);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.05);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .constraint-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0; right: 0;
            width: 4px;
            height: 100%;
            background: var(--card-accent, var(--primary));
            border-radius: 0 var(--radius-card) var(--radius-card) 0;
            opacity: 0;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }
        .constraint-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-6px);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-hover);
        }
        .constraint-card:hover::before { opacity: 1; }

        /* Card colour accents */
        .card-c1  { --card-accent: #1565C0; }
        .card-c2  { --card-accent: #00838F; }
        .card-c3  { --card-accent: #C62828; }
        .card-c4  { --card-accent: #6A1B9A; }
        .card-c5  { --card-accent: #2E7D32; }
        .card-c6  { --card-accent: #E65100; }
        .card-c7  { --card-accent: #4527A0; }
        .card-c8  { --card-accent: #00695C; }
        .card-c9  { --card-accent: #F57F17; }
        .card-c10 { --card-accent: #1B5E20; }
        .card-c11 { --card-accent: #37474F; }
        .card-c12 { --card-accent: #880E4F; }

        .card-header-row {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 22px;
        }
        .card-icon {
            width: 52px;
            height: 52px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            background: var(--primary-pale);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }
        .constraint-card:hover .card-icon {
            background: var(--card-accent, var(--primary));
        }
        .constraint-card:hover .card-icon .material-icons-round {
            color: #fff;
        }
        .card-icon .material-icons-round {
            font-size: 26px;
            color: var(--card-accent, var(--primary));
            transition: var(--transition);
        }
        .card-num {
            font-size: .75rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--card-accent, var(--primary));
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            line-height: 1;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }
        .card-title {
            font-size: 1.15rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--page-text);
            line-height: 1.4;
        }
        .card-sub {
            font-size: .85rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-top: 4px;
        }

        .card-body-text { flex: 1; }

        .card-list {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0 0 24px;
        }
        .card-list li {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 10px;
            font-size: .95rem;
            color: var(--text-sub);
            padding: 8px 0; /* Increased padding */
            border-bottom: 1px dashed rgba(0,0,0,.06);
        }
        body.mode-dark .card-list li { border-color: rgba(255,255,255,.06); }
        .card-list li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
        .card-list li::before {
            content: '◆';
            font-size: .45rem;
            color: var(--card-accent, var(--primary));
            margin-top: 8px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .impact-box {
            margin-top: auto;
            padding: 14px 18px;
            background: rgba(255,111,0,.08);
            border-right: 3px solid var(--accent-warm);
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: .9rem;
            color: var(--accent-warm);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        body.mode-dark .impact-box { background: rgba(255,111,0,.12); }
        .impact-box strong { font-weight: 700; }

        /* =========================================================
           HOVER TRANSLATION TOOLTIP
        ========================================================= */
        .en-term {
            border-bottom: 2px dashed var(--primary);
            cursor: help;
            position: relative;
            display: inline-block;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--primary);
        }
        .en-term::after {
            content: attr(data-ar);
            position: absolute;
            bottom: calc(100% + 8px);
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%) scale(.9);
            background: var(--text-main);
            color: #fff;
            padding: 6px 12px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: .78rem;
            white-space: nowrap;
            font-family: var(--font);
            font-style: normal;
            opacity: 0;
            pointer-events: none;
            transition: opacity .2s ease, transform .2s ease;
            z-index: 100;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(0,0,0,.25);
        }
        .en-term::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: calc(100% + 4px);
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%) scale(.9);
            border: 5px solid transparent;
            border-top-color: var(--text-main);
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity .2s ease, transform .2s ease;
            z-index: 100;
        }
        .en-term:hover::after,
        .en-term:hover::before {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateX(-50%) scale(1);
        }
        body.mode-dark .en-term::after { background: #CDD9E5; color: #0D1117; }
        body.mode-dark .en-term::before { border-top-color: #CDD9E5; }

        /* =========================================================
           SUMMARY SECTION
        ========================================================= */
        .summary-section { margin-top: 80px; }
        .summary-box {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 42px 38px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-card);
        }
        .summary-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(180px, 1fr));
            gap: 24px;
            margin-top: 32px;
        }
        .summary-item {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 24px 18px;
            border-radius: 14px;
            background: var(--primary-pale);
            transition: var(--transition);
        }
        .summary-item:hover {
            transform: translateY(-4px);
            background: var(--primary);
        }
        .summary-item:hover .summary-en,
        .summary-item:hover .summary-ar { color: #fff; }
        .summary-icon { font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
        .summary-en {
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--primary);
            transition: var(--transition);
        }
        .summary-ar {
            font-size: .85rem;
            color: var(--text-sub);
            margin-top: 6px;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }

        /* =========================================================
           FOOTER
        ========================================================= */
        .footer-bar {
            background: #0D1117;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,.6);
            text-align: center;
            padding: 28px;
            margin-top: 80px;
            font-size: .85rem;
        }

        /* =========================================================
           CONTAINER UTILITY
        ========================================================= */
        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        /* =========================================================
           PRINT STYLES
        ========================================================= */
        @media print {
            .mode-switcher, .fab-group { display: none !important; }
            .hero-section { border-radius: 0; }
            .constraint-card { break-inside: avoid; }
            body { background: #fff !important; color: #000 !important; }
        }

        /* =========================================================
           RESPONSIVE
        ========================================================= */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero-section { padding: 70px 0 50px; border-radius: 0 0 32px 32px; margin-bottom: 50px; }
            .hero-stats { gap: 24px; }
            .hero-stat-num { font-size: 1.8rem; }
            .mode-switcher { top: 12px; left: 12px; padding: 5px 8px; gap: 4px; }
            .mode-label { display: none; }
            .fab-group { bottom: 20px; left: 16px; }
            .fab { width: 46px; height: 46px; }
            .summary-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
            .cards-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } /* 1 Column for Mobile */
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .hero-title { font-size: 1.8rem; }
            .summary-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="mode-light">

<div class="mode-switcher" role="group" aria-label="وضع القراءة">
    <span class="mode-label">وضع</span>
    <button class="mode-btn btn-light-mode active" onclick="setMode('light')" title="الوضع العادي" aria-label="الوضع العادي">☀️</button>
    <button class="mode-btn btn-sepia-mode"        onclick="setMode('sepia')" title="وضع سيبيا"   aria-label="وضع سيبيا">📜</button>
    <button class="mode-btn btn-dark-mode"         onclick="setMode('dark')"  title="الوضع الليلي" aria-label="الوضع الليلي">🌙</button>
</div>

<div class="fab-group">
    <button class="fab fab-print"  onclick="window.print()" title="طباعة الصفحة" aria-label="طباعة">
        <span class="material-icons-round">print</span>
    </button>
    <button class="fab fab-top" id="fabTop" onclick="scrollToTop()" title="العودة للأعلى" aria-label="للأعلى">
        <span class="material-icons-round">keyboard_arrow_up</span>
    </button>
</div>

<header class="hero-section" id="top">
    <div class="container" style="text-align:center; position:relative; z-index:1;">
        <span class="badge badge-hero mb-3 px-4 py-2" style="border-radius:999px; display:inline-block;">تحليل مالي استراتيجي</span>
        <h1 class="hero-title mt-2 mb-4">قيود قرارات الاستثمار</h1>
        <p class="hero-sub">ما وراء الأرقام المحاسبية — العوامل الـ 12 الحاسمة التي تحدد مصير المشاريع الاستثمارية في الواقع العملي، ولا تظهر في أي جدول بيانات.</p>

        <div class="hero-stats">
            <div class="hero-stat">
                <div class="hero-stat-num">12</div>
                <div class="hero-stat-lbl">قيد حاسم</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</header>

<main class="container">

    <section>
        <div class="section-heading">
            <div class="section-eyebrow">الدليل التطبيقي الشامل</div>
            <h2 class="section-title">القيود الـ 12 الحاسمة</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="cards-grid">

            <article class="constraint-card card-c1">
                <div class="card-header-row">
                    <div class="card-icon">
                        <span class="material-icons-round">monetization_on</span>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <div class="card-num">01 &mdash; التمويل</div>
                        <div class="card-title">التمويل ورأس المال</div>
                        <div class="card-sub">هل المال متوفر؟ وبأي تكلفة فعلية؟</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <ul class="card-list">
                    <li><span class="en-term" data-ar="ترشيد رأس المال">Capital Rationing</span> — ميزانية استثمارية محدودة تجبر على الاختيار بين مشاريع.</li>
                    <li>ارتفاع أسعار الفائدة يرفع تكلفة <span class="en-term" data-ar="الدين / الاقتراض">Debt</span> ويضغط على العائد الصافي.</li>
                    <li>شروط المقرضين (<span class="en-term" data-ar="اشتراطات تعاقدية">Covenants</span>) تقيّد الاستثمار الجديد أحيانًا.</li>
                </ul>
                <div class="impact-box">
                    <strong>⚡ الأثر العملي:</strong> اختيار مشاريع بعائد أقل لأنها تتناسب مع القدرة التمويلية المتاحة فعلًا.
                </div>
            </article>

            <article class="constraint-card card-c2">
                <div class="card-header-row">
                    <div class="card-icon">
                        <span class="material-icons-round">water_drop</span>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <div class="card-num">02 &mdash; السيولة</div>
                        <div class="card-title">السيولة والتدفقات النقدية</div>
                        <div class="card-sub">الربح محاسبي، أما النقد فحقيقة لا تقبل التأجيل.</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <ul class="card-list">
                    <li>مشاريع تستنزف النقد لسنوات قبل أن تولّد أي عائد (<span class="en-term" data-ar="فترة الاسترداد">Payback Period</span> طويلة).</li>
                    <li>قيود <span class="en-term" data-ar="رأس المال العامل">Working Capital</span> تعيق بدء التشغيل.</li>
                    <li>التزامات تشغيلية عاجلة تعيد ترتيب الأولويات قسرًا.</li>
                </ul>
                <div class="impact-box">
                    <strong>⚡ الأثر العملي:</strong> رفض مشاريع ممتازة ماليًا لحاجة الشركة الفورية لسيولة تشغيلية.
                </div>
            </article>

            <article class="constraint-card card-c3">
                <div class="card-header-row">
                    <div class="card-icon">
                        <span class="material-icons-round">trending_down</span>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <div class="card-num">03 &mdash; المخاطر</div>
                        <div class="card-title">المخاطر وعدم اليقين</div>
                        <div class="card-sub">نطاق النتائج قد يكون واسعًا ومكلفًا.</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <ul class="card-list">
